title: Juelz Santana - Dip'd In Coke Feat. French Montana & Cam'ron (Prod. By Harry Fraud & Maaly Raw)
text: 0 MAKE IT STOP French Montana & Cam'ron hop on Juelz Santana's new song "Dip'd In Coke." Well here it is people. After teasing us heavily on social media these past couple weeks, Juelz Santana decides to finally release his new single with French Montana & Cam’ron called “Dip’d In Coke,” which is expected to see life on Juelz’s upcoming mixtape The Get Back , dropping in the coming days. Going in over sampled production from Harry Fraud & Maaly Raw, take a listen to the 4-minute, NYC connection and share your thoughts on it below. Look for The Get Back to also feature a song with Migos & Capo called "D Up," which is still on the way as well.
